Paper: hep-th/9908191

Date: 1999-08-28

Title: Orthogonal polynomial method and odd vertices in matrix models

Authors: E. Minguzzi

Comments: 13 pages, 3 Postscript figures

Journal-ref: J.Math.Phys. 41 (2000) 3257

We show how to use the method of orthogonal polynomials for integrating, inthe planar approximation, the partition function of one-matrix models with apotential with even or odd vertices, or any combination of them.